00:14:39.920 --> 00:14:40.720
I know

00:14:41.640 --> 00:14:42.680
Though there's no evidence

00:14:43.200 --> 00:14:44.880
it's most likely Xie Jiachang's doing

00:14:45.440 --> 00:14:46.920
Just now you told us all to lay low

00:14:47.680 --> 00:14:49.680
But from what I know about you

00:14:50.440 --> 00:14:52.640
you intend to dismiss everyone

00:14:53.480 --> 00:14:56.120
and stay to confront Xie Jiachang yourself

00:15:02.440 --> 00:15:03.280
How did you know

00:15:04.080 --> 00:15:04.720
In this world

00:15:04.720 --> 00:15:06.800
no one could know you better than I do

00:15:11.240 --> 00:15:12.080
No need to close

00:15:12.720 --> 00:15:14.280
I'll help you deal with Xie Jiachang

00:15:19.080 --> 00:15:22.640
Why do I feel you're not the same as before

00:15:23.080 --> 00:15:23.880
Trust me

00:15:25.200 --> 00:15:26.480
I can help you defeat him

00:15:30.800 --> 00:15:31.680
How do you want to do it

00:15:33.080 --> 00:15:35.000
Give me the ballroom for one year

00:15:36.000 --> 00:15:36.880
At most one month

00:15:37.680 --> 00:15:40.320
I'll make Xie Jiachang's ballroom close down

00:16:25.280 --> 00:16:26.080
We're leaving, boss

00:16:26.600 --> 00:16:28.720
Take it slow, take it slow, thanks for the hard work

00:16:29.840 --> 00:16:31.120
Finally finished

00:16:31.640 --> 00:16:32.880
The boys are dead tired

00:16:33.880 --> 00:16:35.880
Will this renovation style work?

00:16:35.920 --> 00:16:38.280
That's ten thousand I worked so hard to earn

00:16:38.280 --> 00:16:39.640
Don't let it all go down the drain

00:16:43.080 --> 00:16:45.080
You agree, right, Manager Zheng?

00:16:45.880 --> 00:16:46.880
Thanks for the hard work, really

00:16:47.040 --> 00:16:48.000
Hard work? Come on

00:16:48.280 --> 00:16:49.280
Your foot's injured

00:16:50.480 --> 00:16:51.480
Looks pretty serious

00:16:51.920 --> 00:16:53.080
You probably can't walk

00:16:54.040 --> 00:16:54.440
Hey

00:16:54.440 --> 00:16:55.240
Just a little scrape

00:16:55.280 --> 00:16:56.800
I'll just have to carry you back

00:16:56.800 --> 00:16:57.880
Hey, hey, Zheng Nanfeng

00:16:57.880 --> 00:16:58.880
Put me down, hey

00:16:58.880 --> 00:16:59.680
No, wait

00:16:59.840 --> 00:17:00.720
Let go of me

00:17:00.720 --> 00:17:01.520
Hey

00:17:02.800 --> 00:17:03.600
Zheng Nanfeng

00:17:03.720 --> 00:17:05.120
Put me down

00:17:05.520 --> 00:17:07.600
Zheng Nanfeng, are you deaf or what?

00:17:07.840 --> 00:17:08.640
What do you mean?

00:17:12.000 --> 00:17:12.880
What do you mean, huh?

00:17:13.840 --> 00:17:15.400
Hey, hey

00:17:15.640 --> 00:17:16.520
Put me down

00:17:16.520 --> 00:17:17.720
I can walk by myself

00:17:19.640 --> 00:17:21.480
I will never put you down again, for the rest of my life

00:17:21.520 --> 00:17:23.200
Zheng Nanfeng, why are you so stubborn?

00:17:23.200 --> 00:17:24.920
Put me down

00:17:24.920 --> 00:17:25.720
You

00:17:26.800 --> 00:17:28.240
Quite a coincidence, man, huh

00:17:29.320 --> 00:17:30.120
What do you mean?

00:17:31.600 --> 00:17:33.680
Zheng Nanfeng, I've fallen off!

00:17:36.240 --> 00:17:37.400
We're here, we're here

00:17:52.680 --> 00:17:53.880
No, I'm home too

00:17:55.240 --> 00:17:56.480
Get lost

00:18:06.240 --> 00:18:07.320
Then where do I go?

00:18:10.360 --> 00:18:12.600
I miss you

00:18:13.880 --> 00:18:16.520
Whenever dusk falls

00:18:18.240 --> 00:18:20.600
The evening breeze rises

00:18:22.520 --> 00:18:24.760
I miss you

00:18:26.080 --> 00:18:28.440
Life's riddle

00:18:29.960 --> 00:18:32.560
Try not to see it clearly

00:18:34.360 --> 00:18:36.960
Close your eyes

00:18:38.280 --> 00:18:40.160
Don't respond

00:18:42.480 --> 00:18:46.200
The night wind blows and blows

00:18:46.200 --> 00:18:48.840
Go with the wind

00:18:51.400 --> 00:18:54.280
Tonight, child

00:18:55.080 --> 00:18:58.440
Don't cry in secret

00:18:58.440 --> 00:19:02.280
The night wind blows and blows

00:19:02.280 --> 00:19:04.960
Go with the wind

00:19:07.000 --> 00:19:10.320
With nightfall and the stars

00:19:11.480 --> 00:19:14.440
Drift gently to sleep

00:19:14.440 --> 00:19:16.880
Feel the evening breeze